00:42:29,628 --> 00:42:31,128
(Send)

492
00:42:34,828 --> 00:42:36,928
What kind of a writer do you want to be?

493
00:42:37,588 --> 00:42:39,398
I want to be an original writer.

494
00:42:40,628 --> 00:42:42,288
The writer who imitates nobody.

495
00:42:42,788 --> 00:42:46,458
No. The writer whom nobody can imitate.

496
00:42:46,828 --> 00:42:48,028
- Chateaubriand. - Chateaubriand.

