00:44:05,024 --> 00:44:07,124
(We won't be publishing "Chicago Typewriter" this week.)

509
00:44:08,084 --> 00:44:09,084
What?

510
00:44:10,454 --> 00:44:11,754
Is he not well?

511
00:44:14,224 --> 00:44:15,224
("Chicago Typewriter")

512
00:44:16,284 --> 00:44:18,154
The writer's got no backbone.

513
00:44:18,154 --> 00:44:20,624
He's only published 10 episode, and he's already taking time off.

514
00:44:20,624 --> 00:44:23,754
The ghost writer must've gone on a strike. Give him a raise.

515
00:44:23,754 --> 00:44:26,284
If you can't write, bring back your ghost writer.

516
00:44:26,284 --> 00:44:29,084
You idiots.

517
00:44:31,854 --> 00:44:35,224
(Write a comment)

518
00:44:36,184 --> 00:44:39,924
I will wait for you to come back with the amazing 11th episode.

519
00:44:39,924 --> 00:44:42,254
(Post a comment)

520
00:44:46,454 --> 00:44:47,924
What did I just do?

521
00:44:48,984 --> 00:44:51,524
I must be stupid.

522
00:44:52,054 --> 00:44:53,384
I'm such an idiot.

523
00:44:54,954 --> 00:44:58,924
Seol, I am sorry. I'm late.

524
00:44:59,124 --> 00:45:00,784
Did everything go well at the conference?

525
00:45:00,784 --> 00:45:02,484
I was asleep half of the time.

526
00:45:03,384 --> 00:45:06,584
